{
  "id": "adv_main_02_02_03",
  "title": "東京編1章8話",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_serious-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――翌日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――The next day",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.20666666428248104,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "……結論を話す前に、いくつか教えて下さい\nどうして、星見プロダクションなんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Before I give you my decision‚ I have to ask you some questions.\nWhy Hoshimi Productions?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 7.56666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_03-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "それは……なんとしてでも\nこの業界で生き残りたいからです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Because… no matter what it takes‚\nwe want to stay in this industry.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 13
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_03-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "なんであの人は、こんな決断をしたのか\nその理由を直接聞くまでは……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don’t know why he made the decision he did.\nBut until I hear the reason directly from him‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.033333333333346,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_03-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "……一度ならず二度も私を捨てた理由を聞くまでは\nこの業界から消える訳にはいかないんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "until I hear why he abandoned me not once but twice‚\nI can’t afford to disappear from this industry.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.36666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 23.366666666666706
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 26.500000000000007
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "二度も、捨てた？　天動さんを……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Abandoned you… twice? Tendo-san personally?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.500000000000007,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_03-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "……私は……朝倉恭一の、娘なんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I am… Kyoichi Asakura’s daughter.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.85535144805909,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 29.855351448059125
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 34.90535163879391
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_03-stm001.m4a",
      "text": "ええええ～！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What？？？",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.90535163879395,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 36.9053516387939
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_03-stm002.m4a",
      "text": "ほ、ほほ、それ本当なんですか！？\n都市伝説じゃなくて……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "R-r-r-really? Is that true?!\nNot just an urban rumor?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.50535163879394,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 42.772018305460584
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_03-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "瑠依ちゃんから話すんやったら、この場ではもう\n隠さなくてええやろうし……はい、事実です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ since Rui-chan’s let the cat of the bag out‚ I guess we don’t\nneed to keep it a secret anymore… Yes. It’s true.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.70535163879397,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 50.97201811472572
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_03-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "あれ？　でも、{user}さんは\n驚かないんですね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? But‚ {user}-san‚\nwhy aren’t you surprised?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.37201811472576,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 55.329365126291925
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "え！？　ああ、いや……驚いていますよ、十分\n顔に出ないだけで",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh?! Oh‚ uh‚ yeah… of course I’m surprised! Plenty surprised.\nI’m just not showing it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.03879029613805,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_03-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "私がバンプロを選んだ理由も\n社長が実の父だと知ったことが大きいんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A big reason why I chose Van Productions‚\nwas because I found out that the president was my real father.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.2185713132223,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 66.6185713132223
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_03-rui006.m4a",
      "text": "入所後は私を捨てた父の側で、彼でさえ振り向くほどの\nトップアイドルになってみせると努力しました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "After joining‚ I worked hard under the father who abandoned me\nto become a top idol so big he would have to acknowledge me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.7185713132223,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 74.4519046465556
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_03-rui007.m4a",
      "text": "もっとも、道半ばでこんな思ってもみなかった\n仕打ちをされてしまいましたけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I never anticipated this would happen‚\nthat I’d be treated this way halfway through.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.68523797988895,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 80.05190464655557
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "……なるほど、その決意は理解しました。でもそれは\nうちに来る理由にはならないと思うんですけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see. I understand now how determined you are.\nBut that doesn’t serve as a good reason for you to come here.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.55190464655563,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_tension-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 87.65190464655562
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_03-rui008.m4a",
      "text": "正直に言うと\n星見プロだから入りたい訳じゃありません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "To be honest‚\nI don’t want to be signed here because it’s Hoshimi Productions.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.18523797988895,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 92.21857131322228
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_03-rui009.m4a",
      "text": "今、サニピと月ストの側にいられる環境が\n星見プロだった……それが一番の理由です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Right now‚ the only way to be around Sunny Peace and Moon Tempest\nis at Hoshimi Productions. That’s my main reason.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.32942164738976,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_03-rui010.m4a",
      "text": "グランプリで見せてくれたパフォーマンスには\n凄い刺激を受けましたし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Their performances at the Grand Prix\nmoved me deeply‚ too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.17360531489057,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 103.14027202924086
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_03-rui011.m4a",
      "text": "そんな彼女達の側で切磋琢磨出来れば、私達は\nもっともっと上を目指せると……そう思っています",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I thought that if we could learn from each other‚\nwe could strive to reach even greater heights.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.87360536257428,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 110.67360536257462
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_03-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "もちろん、星見プロさんにとっても悪い話やないと\n思います。うちら、一杯仕事取ってきますし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Naturally‚ we think this would be beneficial to Hoshimi Productions‚ too.\nWe can book lots of gigs for you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.14027202924096,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 118.39512483278914
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_03-yu004.m4a",
      "text": "サニピや月ストのみんなにとっても\nいい刺激になるんちゃうかなぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And I think we could really invigorate\neveryone in Sunny Peace and Moon Tempest.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.72777482668562,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 123.26884357134539
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_03-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "だから、星見プロに入れて下さい……っ\nお願いします！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So please‚ let us join Hoshimi Productions!\nPlease!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.86884357134501,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 125.86884357134537
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 128.16884357134506
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
