      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_03-chs003.m4a",
      "text": "ず、ズルいって……そういうつもりじゃなくって\n少しだけ、会って話したことがあったから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I d-didn’t mean to do anything unfair.\nI just talked with her a little once.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 303.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_03-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "大丈夫よ、雫ちゃん\n私達だって、これから親睦を深めていけばいいんだし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don’t worry‚ Shizuku-chan.\nThe rest of us will have plenty of chances to get to know them.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 309.8666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_03-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "まあ、ズルいって思うのも分かりますけど。レベルの\n高い人との交流は、それだけでも刺激になりますし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ I can see why you’d consider it unfair.\nJust interacting with high-level people does really provide stimulation.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 318.6666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_03-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "最初は不安に思ったけど……今回のことは\n私達にとっても成長のチャンスってこと、なのかな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was worried at first… but now‚\nI think this new development is an opportunity for us all to grow.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 326.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_03-rui022.m4a",
      "text": "ええ。そうしてお互いを高めていけるなら\nそれが理想だと、私も思っているわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes. If we can help each other improve‚\nI think that would be ideal.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 334.6666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_03-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "……分かりました。勉強させていただきます\n改めて、よろしくお願いします、天動さん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Understood. I look forward to learning from you.\nOnce again‚ welcome to the agency‚ Tendo-san.",
